', '   \item What is the radius of a circle with circumference 100.5, rounded to the \emph{nearest hundredth}? \vspace{4cm}
', '
', '  \item Circle $O$ has a radius $AO=11$ cm, as shown below, and arc measure $m \wideparen{AB}=105^\circ$.
